title: Ibrahimovic's Sweden faces Denmark in Euros playoff derby
text:
FREDRIK SANDBERG/TT Ibrahimovic's Sweden faces Denmark in Euros playoff derby 
Sweden's Zlatan Ibrahimovic celebrates scoring the opening goal during the UEFA Euro 2016 group G qualifying soccer match between Sweden and Moldova at Friends Arena in Stockholm, Sweden, on Monday Oct. 12, 2015. (Fredrik Sandberg / TT via AP) SWEDEN OUT Posted: Sunday, October 18, 2015 6:16 am Ibrahimovic's Sweden faces Denmark in Euros playoff derby Associated Press | 
NYON, Switzerland (AP) — Zlatan Ibrahimovic's Sweden will face Denmark in a Nordic derby in the Euro 2016 playoffs. 
Norway, another Nordic nation chasing one of the remaining four spots at the expanded 24-team tournament, was drawn Sunday to play Hungary in the two-legged playoffs next month.
